---
import Tool from '../../layouts/Tool.astro';
---

<Tool
	title="Image Converter – PNG to JPG & WEBP | SinzTools"
	description="Convert images between PNG, JPG, and WEBP formats quickly and for free. No upload required - works directly in your browser."
	tool="image-converter"
>
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
<h1>Image Converter</h1>
<p>Convert your images between PNG, JPG, and WEBP formats instantly in your browser. No uploads to servers - your files stay private and secure.</p>
<h2>How to Use</h2>
<p>Select an image file, choose the desired output format, and click Convert. Your converted image will be ready for download.</p>

<div class="privacy-note">
	<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon">
		<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.623 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z"/>
	</svg>
	Runs locally — no uploads. Your images never leave your device.
</div>

<div class="drop-zone" id="dropZone">
	<input type="file" id="fileInput" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/webp" required style="display: none;">
	<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon">
		<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 16.5V9.75m0 0 3 3m-3-3-3 3M6.75 19.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.41-8.775 5.25 5.25 0 0 1 10.233-2.33 3 3 0 0 1 3.758 3.848A3.752 3.752 0 0 1 18 19.5H6.75Z"/>
	</svg>
	<p>Drop an image here or <label for="fileInput">browse</label></p>
</div>

<div id="fileInfo" style="display: none; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
	<strong>Selected file:</strong> <span id="fileName"></span> (<span id="fileSize"></span>)
</div>

<label for="formatSelect">Output Format:</label>
<select id="formatSelect">
	<option value="png">PNG</option>
	<option value="jpg">JPG</option>
	<option value="webp">WEBP</option>
</select>
<br><br>
<button type="button" id="convertBtn">Convert Image</button>

<div id="errorMessage" class="error-message"></div>
<div id="output"></div>
<h2>How this Image Converter works</h2>
<p>This tool uses your browser's built-in canvas technology to convert images between formats. When you select a file, it's processed locally without uploading to any server, ensuring fast and secure conversions.</p>
<h2>Supported formats & privacy</h2>
<p>We support PNG, JPG, and WEBP formats. All processing happens in your browser - your images never leave your device, keeping your files completely private.</p>
